"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/929386","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2018-06-28","<p>Neither the Department nor its arm’s length bodies hold the information requested.</p>","Thurrock","Jackie Doyle-Price","156615 ; 156616","2018-06-28T14:56:47.95Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/929386/answer","Biography information for Jackie Doyle-Price","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/929386/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/929386/answer",,,,,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2018-06-22","Plastic Surgery","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, how much the NHS has spent on corrective surgery performed on private cosmetic patients in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","156614"
